title: U.S. ready to open Jerusalem embassy in May
text:
U.S. ready to open Jerusalem embassy in May 9:03pm GMT - 01:04 
The United States said on Friday it will open its embassy to Israel in Jerusalem in May, a move from Tel Aviv that reverses decades of U.S. policy. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
